  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>♠</u></strong><u> <strong>♥ ♦ ♣  Welcome to Durak Online!  ♣ ♦ ♥  ♠</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Durak is a fast-paced, strategic card game originating from Russia, renowned for its simplicity and depth. Playable with 2 - 6 players, Durak challenges participants to outwit their opponents and avoid becoming the titular \"Durak\" or \"fool\" — the player left with cards when everyone else is finished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Durak is easy to pick up but rewards clever strategies and bold decisions. With its mix of luck, skill, and the joy of watching others scramble under pressure,   it is a classic staple in card game culture worldwide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with strangers or friends, or offline with bots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ranked with elo and fixed rules will be addad a few weeks after release when everything is running smoothly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u>The following settings are adjustable:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number of cards (24, 36, 52)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheating on / off</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only neighbours can attack / Everyone can attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw-Ins allowed / Throw-Ins not allowed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Timer normal / fast</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similarly, other graphical customizations that are unlocked in the game over time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Card Decks:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/fd479d39c902e93698b4fc8314bdd929.poster.avif?t=1764674172\" width=800 height=207 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/fd479d39c902e93698b4fc8314bdd929.webm?t=1764674172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Backsides:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/3848efe484fac2dbca818d93f0d7ba7c.poster.avif?t=1764674172\" width=188 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/3848efe484fac2dbca818d93f0d7ba7c.webm?t=1764674172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Backgrounds:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/26d5590743cbf529545565810f775b83.poster.avif?t=1764674172\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/26d5590743cbf529545565810f775b83.webm?t=1764674172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Playerprofiles (visible to other players):</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/688360d6a47d3f18ccc091128e9d0716.poster.avif?t=1764674172\" width=800 height=135 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/extras/688360d6a47d3f18ccc091128e9d0716.webm?t=1764674172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and a lot more in the future!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>♠</u></strong><u> <strong>♥ ♦ ♣  Welcome to Durak Online!  ♣ ♦ ♥  ♠</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Durak is a fast-paced, strategic card game originating from Russia, renowned for its simplicity and depth. Playable with 2 - 6 players, Durak challenges participants to outwit their opponents and avoid becoming the titular \"Durak\" or \"fool\" — the player left with cards when everyone else is finished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Durak is easy to pick up but rewards clever strategies and bold decisions. With its mix of luck, skill, and the joy of watching others scramble under pressure,   it is a classic staple in card game culture worldwide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with strangers or friends, or offline with bots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ranked with elo and fixed rules will be addad a few weeks after release when everything is running smoothly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u>The following settings are adjustable:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number of cards (24, 36, 52)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheating on / off</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only neighbours can attack / Everyone can attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw-Ins allowed / Throw-Ins not allowed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Timer normal / fast</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similarly, other graphical customizations that are unlocked in the game over time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Card Decks:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291790/ext